# 📊 Time Series Forecasting using LSTM (Deep Learning)

## 🚀 Overview

This project implements a **Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM)** neural network to perform time series forecasting. 
The model learns patterns from sequential data and predicts future values based on historical trends.

This project demonstrates strong skills in **deep learning, sequence modeling and predictive analytics**, 
Making it highly relevant for real-world applications like stock price prediction, demand forecasting and anomaly detection.

---

## 🎯 Problem Statement

Time series data is widely used across industries, but traditional models often fail to capture long-term dependencies.

👉 This project solves that by:

* Using LSTM networks to capture temporal dependencies
* Learning patterns from past sequences
* Predicting future values accurately

---

## 🧠 Model Architecture

* Input Layer (Time Series Sequences)
* LSTM Layer (captures temporal dependencies)
* Dense Layer (output prediction)

---

## ⚙️ Technologies Used

* Python
* NumPy
* TensorFlow / Keras
